query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `fechamentos_mensais` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
  `mes` int NOT NULL,
  `ano` int NOT NULL,
  `tipo` enum('vendas','conta_bancaria') NOT NULL,
  `receitaCartoes` decimal(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `receitaPix` decimal(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `receitaDinheiro` decimal(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `receitaRendimento` decimal(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `receitaPlataforma` decimal(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `receitaPagseguro` decimal(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `receitaSantander` decimal(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `despesaTarifaCartao` decimal(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `despesaOutrasTarifas` decimal(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `despesaImpostos` decimal(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `despesaMaquiadora` decimal(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `despesaOperacaoFora` decimal(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `despesaInvestimentos` decimal(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `despesaEstorno` decimal(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `despesaTransfSantander` decimal(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `impostosIss` decimal(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `impostosPis` decimal(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `impostosCofins` decimal(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `impostosCsll` decimal(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `impostosIrpj` decimal(15,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `aliquotaIrpjEstimada` decimal(5,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `aliquotaIrpjReal` decimal(5,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `criadoPorId` int NOT NULL,
  `criadoPorNome` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `createdAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `updatedAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  CONSTRAINT `fechamentos_mensais_id` PRIMARY KEY(`id`)
)
